oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Blues Traveler at the Red Socks Amphitheater
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Rock groups; Rock music; Blues Traveler (Musical group); Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (blue, red and white on tan) announcing Blues Traveler, an American rock band, at the Red Rock Amphitheater on July 4. Poster features woodcuts of a cat head and a cinema block print popularized in the 1950s.
